# Standard .gitignore template for C++, Python, VS Code on macOS & Windows

# ============================
# 1. OS specific files
# ============================
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
*.log

# ============================
# 2. Local Editor/IDE Settings (隔离跨端配置)
# ============================
.vscode/
.idea/
settings.json
*.swp

# ============================
# 3. C/C++ 编译产物 (物理拦截机器码)
# ============================
# 忽略所有可执行和目标文件后缀
*.exe
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
*.o
*.obj
*.app
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
bin/

# 【精准狙击：从你的截图来看，当前已存在的无后缀 Linux 编译产物】
C/day1
C/day1_2
C/day2
C/day3
C/day4
C/day5
C/day6
C/hello
C/lp
C/main
C/run_me
C/test
C/tranf

# ============================
# 4. Python 环境与缓存
# ============================
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.venv/
venv/
*.ipynb_checkpoints